items.name: Glider Suit Skin
items.description: When attached to a Chest Armor, the Glider Suit enables sailing through the air by double-tapping jump, while gaining speed by running and diving!

items.name: SF Griffin Charm
items.description: Equip a Griffin with this (it fits right in the costume slot) to give it some protective armor.

items.name: SF Phoenix Charm
items.description: Equip a Phoenix with this (it fits right in the costume slot) to give it some protective armor.

items.name: Rock Drake Tek Saddle
items.description:
Equip a Rock Drake with this to ride it, enabling the rider to fire plasma projectiles.
Using requires learning this Tekgram (SF)

items.name: SF Wyvern Charm
items.description: Equip a Wyvern with this (it fits right in the costume slot) to give it some protective armor.
